name: Vennominon the King of Poisonous Snakes
text: This card cannot be Special Summoned by another Effect Monster's effect. This card is unaffected by "Venom Swamp". This card gains 500 ATK for each Repitile-Type monster in your Graveyard. When this card is destroyed by battle and sent to the Graveyard, you can remove from play 1 other Repitile-Type monster from your Graveyard to Special Summon this card.
